<p><div align="center"><table width="50%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Bombus tucumanus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Vachal, 1904</font></b><br>
<small><i>Bombus weisi albocaudata </i>Friese, 1903; <i>Bombus robustus var cinctus </i>Friese, 1904; <i>Bombus robustus var rufocaudatus </i>Friese, 1904; <i>Bombus robustus var steinbachi </i>Friese, 1908; <i>Bombus robustus var sulfuratus </i>Friese, 1911; <i>Bombus &#40;Robustobombus&#41; albocaudatus </i>Friese, 1903; <i>Pyrobombus &#40;Cullumanobombus&#41; tucumanus </i>&#40;Vachal, 1904&#41;</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Hymenoptera">Hymenoptera</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apoidea">Apoidea</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Apidae">Apidae</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Bombus">Bombus</a>
<br><small>Subgenus: <a href="/mp/20p?see=Cullumanobombus&name=Bombus&flags=subgenus:"><i>Cullumanobombus</i></a></small>
