<div align="center">
<table><tr><td valign="top" align="center"><a href="/mp/20m?kind=Bombus+tucumanus"><img src="/nh/maps/Insecta/Hymenoptera/Apoidea/Apidae/Bombus/map_of_Bombus_tucumanus.jpg" width="360" height="180" border="0"></a><br><font color="red" size="-1" face="sans-serif">Click on map for details about points.</font>
<p><div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="50%"><tr><td nowrap><b>IDnature guide</b></td></tr><tr><td nowrap><ul><li><a href="/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species&flags=HAS:" target="_top">
Bee species</a></li>
